WEBVTT

00:00:06.793 --> 00:00:08.921
Kroz istoriju čovečanstva,

00:00:08.921 --> 00:00:12.384
tri male reči vodile su pesnike 
do prazne stranice,

00:00:12.384 --> 00:00:14.762
filozofe u agoru

00:00:14.762 --> 00:00:17.102
a tragače u proročišta -

00:00:17.102 --> 00:00:19.099
„ko sam ja?”

00:00:19.099 --> 00:00:22.723
Počevši od starogrčkog aforizma 
zapisanog na Apolonovom hramu,

00:00:22.723 --> 00:00:24.459
„Spoznaj samoga sebe”,

00:00:24.459 --> 00:00:27.192
do rok himne „Ko si ti?” grupe „Hu”,

00:00:27.192 --> 00:00:30.312
filozofi, psiholozi, akademici,